TopicTitle: KSO Shuttle Mod Missions: STS 104 Minmus Science Rover Deployment and Landing

Articles.Content:
The Fourth of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions! STS 104's objectives are to deploy the Minmus Science Rover, return to the KSC, and successfully land the rover on Minmus.

Most of the footage is shown in 4x speed for quick viewing.

STS 105 Will bring a Kerbal to the Mun and back!

Get the mods!
